      108.02,
      73.57,
      526.34,
      128.25
    ],
    "text": "On 18.04.2026, officers of the Walana Central Anti-Corruption Unit conducted a raid in the Godigamuwa area of the Moragahahena Police Division and arrested a suspect with 1125 liters (150 bottles) of illegal liquor and presented him to the Moragahahena Police Station.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
